<h2>shelff JSON Specification</h2>

<p>shelff stores metadata and reading progress for PDF files as JSON files in iCloud. This page describes the specification of the JSON files that shelff reads and writes.</p>

<p>shelff manages its data through these JSON files. Other tools can interoperate with shelff by reading and writing the same files.</p>

